title: Best of CCK: Car Trouble
description:
KFC is the King of Inconvenience, this time his brand new Hyundai Tucson breaks down for no reason. Could Brandon Walker beat up Carrabis? Could Feitelberg beat up Vladimir Putin? Dinner with the D'Amelios goes horribly wrong.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
